data.description: This charming three (3) bedroom, two (2) bath home in the Boyds Creek area comes with the sought after mountain views and nearly a full acre to create the space you have been dreaming of. This home is move  in ready. Home offers a new cozy fireplace, a very spacious kitchen and formal dining room. The primary bedroom suite comes with a walk in closet. Relax on your covered patio while listening to the sounds of nature. This is the perfect location, close to Seymour, Sevierville, Knoxville, Pigeon Forge and Gatlinburg area. Restaurants, grocery stores and shopping all near by. Come take a look at what this amazing property has to offer.
